    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll slimes to solve puzzles on your adventure in an odd little village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/94c820642f10a2e55f68f43e331d2ea5.poster.avif?t=1748571193\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/94c820642f10a2e55f68f43e331d2ea5.webm?t=1748571193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/94c820642f10a2e55f68f43e331d2ea5.mp4?t=1748571193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roll the blue slime into the goal to unlock the path to the next area.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sometimes, moving stuff around will also move the story along!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight enemies in puzzle battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Blue Slime Village, the stage for this puzzle game, where you'll find gimmicks galore!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/f6aa823988363b29aa0e4442819b63ce.poster.avif?t=1748571193\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/f6aa823988363b29aa0e4442819b63ce.webm?t=1748571193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/f6aa823988363b29aa0e4442819b63ce.mp4?t=1748571193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls are simple. Enjoy a variety of puzzle gimmicks just by moving around.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time to think with the puzzles. There's no need to rush your actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use hints if you run into a puzzle that you just can't figure out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Listen to the original chiptune soundtrack by HaL_Bits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/f5944949bded6383d3dbf6c5e7e74cab.poster.avif?t=1748571193\" width=616 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/f5944949bded6383d3dbf6c5e7e74cab.webm?t=1748571193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/f5944949bded6383d3dbf6c5e7e74cab.mp4?t=1748571193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>There are a lot more fun things to discover!</p></li></ul>",
